Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 再忍耐一下就能完成封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力完成最後一段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天 後面有怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西前輩 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些糾纏不清的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 那種狀態下 物理攻擊是無法奏效的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連我的蟲子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些麻煩的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還是交給兩位上忍比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心是不是指這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟兒到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就成了我的收藏品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個非常難纏的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接去跟大蛇丸大人聯繫也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為你的手下 已經工作了很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧大蛇丸大人 我一個人就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 一切都是照你的計劃進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 大蛇丸大人果然是位優秀的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情全都朝著大蛇丸大人預計的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓紅蓮和幽鬼丸相互信任 將對方視為歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦受到挑撥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸就能爆發出強大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應如此才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 告知紅蓮是其殺母仇人後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸的怨恨也沒能爆發出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的內心真是非常不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把幽鬼丸和紅蓮的感情當作什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的感情可不是你們的玩物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是木葉和曉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後 各個忍村間也會開始相互廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人正是預見了這樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會如此需要三尾的力量 還有幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說一些莫名其妙的廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶幽鬼丸離開 一定要保護好他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 哪怕用性命來交換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想過我這關 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你嘗嘗苦頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死魂之術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好的 一定會保護好你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶遁.紅之果實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 很快就會回到你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會回來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歸宿只剩紅蓮姐一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我還死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這招對我起不了作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總的來說 結晶就是同樣的多面體物質
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整齊一致地排列而生成的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在形成結晶的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠所發出的超聲波使周圍的空氣震動開來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣便可瓦解其形成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實一開始 你的晶遁之術就不是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就說過沒用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便死了依然這麼煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理完紅蓮就該你了 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算豁出性命 我也要保住幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的晶遁已經沒有作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對死人做什麼都是白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就無法控制蝙蝠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶遁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實地回黃泉去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術被破解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要一直守護幽鬼丸的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該進行封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三尾到底從哪兒得到這麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三尾的查克拉突然急速增長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 用木遁牽制住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我來了結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快尋找封印班 支援他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三尾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了重要的紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在幽鬼丸身上的力量終於爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到失去歸宿的悲憤竟然如此強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸 能聽到嗎 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 快清醒過來 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都給我毀滅吧 毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸也派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是風遁.螺旋手裡劍又無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 那不是三尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又被捲入到麻煩事裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我也不會召你們出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆龍 準備蛤蟆鐵炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 蛤蟆龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 現在可是事態緊急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是生活在湖中的巨大龜型尾獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說風遁可以提升威力 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但水遁的蛤蟆鐵炮能起多大作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想戰勝水遁就需要土遁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒時間再磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會使用風遁 沒辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來我和佐助的優劣關係不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠贏雷的只有風了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓火變得更加強大的只有風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是火遁的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁嗎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是火遁的話 就能夠借助我的風…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用火遁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又沒問我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有火遁的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 還以為是個好點子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼嘛 說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 只有風能助長火勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可火還是弱於水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那就以超水遁的火力將水蒸發不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回村子去 喝滿蛤蟆油再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 僅限一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘之後就把你召喚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以油代水來發射蛤蟆鐵炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將油擴散後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以蛤蟆吉的火遁點燃油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能按照蛤蟆鐵炮的同樣模式發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不需要練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮 你未能完成的約定就由我來完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 一分鐘過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個新的復合忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準對方臉部 其弱點就是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始 不容有失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 蛤蟆龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復合忍法.蛤蟆油炎彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 成功了啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來暫時告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的出現在預測之外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…紅蓮也死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜啊 她本是個擁有特殊之力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是些違心的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外關於幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到佐助的身體就行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸宿
